products.title: Gecko Aluminium Venetian
products.description: This matt effect, powder green venetian blind is calm, cool and collected. Use this to help bring some tranquillity to a room. Perfect for a bathroom or kitchen this venetian blind will give you full control over the light entering your home. Keep your blinds looking their best with their easy to wipe clean aluminium slats, just use a damp cloth to wipe away any dirt or stains.
